on.</span><hr size=1> Scenario:<br>
<br>
One computer.<br>
<br>
Two ethernet cards with active TCP/IP connections to the internet.<br>
<br>
Is it possible to set up some sort of auto-routing system where if one link goes down, the other can automatically be switched to?<br>
<br>
